* 2011 - Best Screenplay Award from Arpa Film Festival for [[My Uncle Rafael]] screenplay <ref name="salamtoronto" /><ref name="arpa" />
* 2011 - Audience Choice Award from Pomegranate Film Festival in Toronto for the movie [[My Uncle Rafael]]<ref name="salamtoronto" />
* 2013 - Golden Pom Award from Pomegranate Film Festival in Toronto for the movie ''Guardian Angel (2014)'' <ref name="pom" />
* 2015 - World Armenian Entertainment Awards <ref name="armentaward">{{cite web|url=http://lafashionjudge.com/the-2nd-annual-world-armenian-entertainment-awards-2015-red-carpet/|work=LA Fashion Judge|title=World Armenian Entertainment Awards 2015|accessdate=May 14, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706044555/http://lafashionjudge.com/the-2nd-annual-world-armenian-entertainment-awards-2015-red-carpet/|archive-date=2015-07-06|dead-url=no|df=}}</ref>

